Wednesday, November 16, 2016








Morty Davis with President-elect Trump











A
great picture of Morty Davis and his grandson Jamie with President-elect Donald
Trump, who praised Morty’s universally admired book From Hard Rocks to Hot
Stocks saying, “Morty Davis has written a chronicle of great triumphs….full
of intriguing speculation and clear insights, provocative, challenging and
enlightening and written by a unique man who really knows the score. A must
read!”



Not
as concise as Larry King’s endorsement, “This is the best book I’ve ever read
on making it big. You’re in the hands of a master. Enjoy.”



In
addition, President Reagan profusely praised Morty’s earlier book Making
America Work Again, whose name President-elect Trump obviously appreciated since
he adopted and paraphrased the title of that brilliant book almost word for
word by using the slogan, “Making America Great Again” in his winning campaign.





