J. Morton and Rosalind Davis Endowed Scholarship Fund





In 1971, Morty and Rozi Davis made a gift to the Mount Sinai School of Medicine to endow a four year merit medical scholarship every four years (providing for a fixed amount per year).  Over the years this endowment has grown and recently three worthy medical students have been recipients of this generous scholarship.





