Morton Thiokol Inc. (MTI) is best known for its role in the fatal space                             shuttle Challenger explosion that killed six                             astronauts and schoolteacher Christa McAuliffe in Cape Canaveral,                             Florida. MTI supplied the National Aeronautics and Space Administration     ...


